memory: Perfect sweet potato soup to get over a cold.
Moroccan donuts

Went insane at the bus stop.
Pretty. Crowded.

Amazing dinner in a suburban family's backyard with other tourists.

Nostalgia. Elisha had her first bistecca della fiorentina.
Ok we are really tired now.

Manic British tour guide. Did I mention how tired we are?
